These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, dubstep
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, peas
1. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person eating peas##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Music-Genre       | dubstep       | trance |
| Beverage         | water | mirinda  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Food   | peas       | eggplant      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, lily
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, pakistani
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
2 different games are played: bridge, chess
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the indian is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Flower      | lily     | amaryllis |
| Nationality           | indian | pakistani      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Game         | bridge | chess     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, gardening
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, baccarat
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, may
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby      | chess | gardening  |
| Cigar          | ritmeester    | baccarat   |
| Birthday   | may  | april   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
House: ranch-style, victorian
2 different pets are kept: cat, bird
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, red
1. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| House          | victorian         | ranch-style    |
| Pet           | bird | cat    |
| Color   | pink           | red   |

 #################################

 
