.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, october
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, grey
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
There 2 different types of food: onion, avocado
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Birthday           | october | september     |
| Color   | brown          | grey |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Food     | avocado            | onion       |

 